===
robinwinslow.co.uk
===

This repository contains all the files for my website.

On my server these files are located in /var/www/robinwinslow.co.uk.

The repository currently contains all the client-side resources (images, css, js) as well as several versions of template files - including raw HTML files, some PHP template files and some json-template files. Also included currently are controllers for serving the content from the json-template files with a PHP controller or a node.js controller.

In the future I'm to move the controller away from this directory, so this repository will only contain client-side resources and json-template files. I will keep the controller code in a separate repository.

